channel.title: XN - The 4th Dimension [Trap] (Interstellar inspired)
channel.description:
Wow a new track that's not for a competition for once.
Was thinking of the Interstellar theme melody and couldn't get it out of my head, so I figured I should make a track around it. It's not a ridiculously complex track and honestly it could probably use a better mixing job, but I know that if I don't decide to push it out now, I won't do it ever. *Thinks back to the 20+ finished tracks that have never been released*
https://soundcloud.com/xn-extras/the-4th-dimension ![Tesseractpavan-glitched-square%201000x1000|500x500](upload://8Ev3LeH1mJ9KSqAYlG5GtkaTdpC.jpeg)
Also on YouTube: https://youtu.be/Ek9_WmwaDfk
